{"tid":2457022,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台東志航空軍基地發生訓練意外 F-5E機師羅尚樺中尉殉職","createTime":"2021-03-22T10:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:43:48.000Z","uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e18be7c365333887ffd3677e65a4f67aaa2e06fc","tid":2457022,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"台東志航空軍基地2架F-5E戰機今天下午執行訓練任務時失聯，軍方指出，此次訓練為4架編隊飛行，其中2、4號機碰撞後落海，2飛行員跳傘，下午4時在海上發現中尉羅尚樺，經送台東馬偕醫院搶救，宣告不治，羅尚樺3月初剛結婚。持續搜尋失聯的上尉潘穎諄。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103225007.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202103225007.aspx&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=0d5b8f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103225007.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"a3bd2c1d3c7faacea8fab3f1e9cde694c6ef8bfc","tid":2457022,"uid":291921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53463ee961f0836f877c57cd47ff1c9f2d9ca155","tid":2457022,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bee9849e2b171d92aef46b5e13603449e23a5e","tid":2457022,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"呢排台灣啲戰機成日出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69300bb1e9c8e5844b9bd9c966f626ce6b9496e1","tid":2457022,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"b3eabe977f9eb0460da5515314d4545d6dc66adc","tid":2457022,"uid":177510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"